<DOC>
<DOCNO>WT16-B25-12</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA022-000239-B035-19</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.sbsc.org:80/claremont/edit/restcon.htm 204.71.237.86 19970108040219 text/html 6822
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 04:02:37 GMT
