<DOCHDR>
http://www.sbsc.org:80/savers/library/current.html 204.71.237.86 19970108052758 text/html 3989
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 05:28:17 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 07-Mar-96 17:47:32 GMT
Content-length: 3801
