<title>October 1996 Washington Watch Newsletter</title>

<body>

<center>
<img src="/townhall/FRC/wwatch/wwatch.gif">
</center>

<p>

Volume 8<br>
Number 1<br>
October 25, 1996

<p><hr width=60% size=3><p>

<center>
<h2>CONTENTS</h2>
</center>

<font size=+1>

