      <td height=132></td>
      <td colspan=2></td>
      <td width=420 height=132 colspan=10 rowspan=1 valign=top align=left>

<p align=left><font face="Arial" size=2>The College of Business (COB) at <a href="http://www.isu.edu">Idaho State University</a></font><font face="Arial" size=2> (ISU) offers a programs leading to both bachelors and Masters of Business Administration. The MBA is available to holders of business and non-business bachelor&#39;s degrees. Both programs are accredited by the American Assembly of Collegiate Schools of Business (AACSB). ISU&#39;s MBA program was the first to be accredited by the AACSB in the State of Idaho and we remain committed to the delivery of a high quality, rigorous program.</p></font>


      </td>
      <td></td>
    </tr>
