<p align=left><font face="Arial" size=2>Accounting has been called the &#39;language of business.&#39; The concepts and terms of accounting are used to describe and measure the events of daily business activity</p></font>


      </td>
      <td></td>
      <td></td>
      <td width=194 height=93 colspan=3 rowspan=1 valign=top align=left>

<p align=left><font face="Arial" size=2>The goal of the Marketing Department is to meet the needs of students interested in marketing careers in local, national and international organizations.</p></font>


