      <td colspan=12></td>
      <td width=306 height=111 colspan=4 rowspan=3 valign=top align=left>

<p align=left><font face="Arial" size=2>The Associate dean and his office admits students to the undergraduate program, determines the applicability of transfer credit to business programs, provides for any exceptions from stated degree requirements, and performs graduation degree audits.</p></font>


