<p align=left><font face="Arial" size=2>The Executive Committee consists of the Deans, the MBA and Accounting Directors, and the five Department Chairs. It provides stability and continuity in the decision making processes of the College by raising questions and offering advice and council to the Dean regarding College operations.</p></font>


