<td>

<p align=center><center><B><font face="Arial" size=3>Idaho State University College of Business Web <br>
</B></font><B><font face="Arial" size=5>CoB-Web</center></p></B></font>


<img width=128 height=171 border=2 src="img1.gif" align=right>

<p align=left><font face="Arial" size=2>Idaho State University&#39;s College of Business offers the highest quality business education. Both its undergraduate and graduate programs are nationally accredited by the American Assembly of Collegiate Schools of Business. The College of Business is committed to providing the business training needed by those entering today&#39;s complex economy. It also equips graduates with the skills needed to meet the challenges presented by a constantly-changing business environment.</p></font>

<br clear="all">
<p>      
<p align=left><font face="Arial" size=2>High-Quality instruction is a trademark of the ISU College of Business. The&nbsp; faculty averages over fifteen years teaching experience per faculty member, over 85&#37; hold a doctoral degree in their specific field. Additional faculty qualifications, including professional business experience, professional certifications, published research papers, articles and books, and other accomplishments, enrich the courses they teach. <br>
<br>
The College of Business has a commitment to students. At ISU, students are provided easy access to expert guidance in their studies. The faulty has an active concern for the progress of every student and works to help students meet their career objectives.</p></font>

