<DOCHDR>
http://gandalf.isu.edu:80/page15.html 134.50.5.16 19970207225006 text/html 4069
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Microsoft-IIS/3.0
Date: Fri, 07 Feb 1997 22:50:17 GMT
