<TITLE>Compaq Computer Corporation</TITLE>
<HEAD></HEAD>
<BODY BACKGROUND="../gifs/grayrock.gif">
<IMG SRC="compaq.gif" ALIGN=LEFT> 
<FONT SIZE=6> Computer Corporation</FONT SIZE=6>
<BR CLEAR=ALL>
<P>


<HR>
<P>
Research  partners come in many forms. Compaq has participated in a unique
relationship by providing resources that normally would be unavailable to
our college of business.
<P>
Compaq has been an important contributor to both the Idaho State University
and the <A HREF="../cds/cds.html">Simplot Decision Support Center</A>.
<P>
For the last two years they have loaned us hardware for use with our
portable decision support center, our information security initiative and
our software engineering program.
<P>
It has afforded our students a unique opportunity to work with equipment
from a state of the art hardware manufacturer.
<P>
Their partnership has allowed us to provide 13 students with scholarships
and research assistantships.
<P>
Computer Science and Computer Information Systems students have linked
portions of the Compaq home pages that they have found interesting to our
system:
<UL>
<LI>Compaq's <A HREF="HTTP://WWW.COMPAQ.COM/cgi-bin/present/graphics/
corporateoverview/history_and_milestones.html>History</A>.
<LI>Take a look at Compaq's powerful and elegant
<A HREF="http://www.compaq.com/gifs/2elitet.gif"><B>notebook computers</B></A>.
<LI>Compaq donated computers to the College of Business from its 
<A HREF="http://www.compaq.com/gifs/dprobigt.gif">
Deskpro Family:<IMG SRC="http://www.compaq.com/gifs/dprofamilyt.gif"
ALIGN=TOP BORDER="0"></A><BR CLEAR=ALL>
<P>
<LI>Visit the <A HREF="http://www.compaq.com/"><IMG SRC="compaq.gif" ALIGN=BOTTOM
BORDER="0" ALT="Compaq"> Home Page</A>.
</UL>
