<BODY BGCOLOR="FFFFFF">
<H1>C-Systems</H1>
<HR>
<P>
C-Systems is a small company which has over the past 10 years 
licensed its interactive technology to the <A HREF="../cds/cds.html">Simplot Decision 
Support Center</A> and Idaho State University. C-System's gifts and in-kind contrubutions are valued at over $115,000.
<P>


