<TITLE>Mason and Hanger National</TITLE><HEAD>
</HEAD>
<BODY BACKGROUND="../gifs/grayrock.gif">
<H1>Mason and Hanger National</H1>
<HR>
<P>
Located in Huntsville, Alabama, Mason and Hanger National provides security systems which utilize laser technology. The system equipment is sufficiently sensitive to detect people walking in a protected area.
<P>
Mason and Hanger National has a subsidary, PEAT, which builds Plasma technology waste systems. The technology deals wuth wastes ranging from high explosives to medical waste.  Their technology is in use by many companies and federal agencies, including the U.S. Department of Energy.
<P>
Mason and Hanger National has donated examples of their systems to the College of Business at Idaho State University, allowing for many students to access state-of-the-art technology.
<P>
</BODY>

