<TITLE>U.S. Department of Education</TITLE>
<HEAD>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="FFFFFF">
<IMG ALIGN=LEFT SRC="bus.gif"><BR><H1>U.S. Department of Education</H1>
<HR>
<P>
The College of Business at Idaho State University is the repository for a classic scheduling program 
developed by the Department of Education. Not only do we 
support the original Fortran progam and documentation, but we 
also have students developing new interfaces and human factors 
models for working with scheduling systems.
<P>
This model has provided unequaled opportunities for our 
students to work with "real world" problems.
<P>
We must also thank Murray Spitzer and John Tressler from the 
U.S. Department of Education for making this opportunity possible.
<P>


