<h1><img src="images/group.gif" align=bottom width=688 height=54></h1>
<h1>Web Starting Points for Information on Groupware</h1>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.crew.umich.edu/~brinck/cscw.html">Tom's CSCW and Groupware Index</a> </li>
<li><a href="http://www.cadre.nepean.uws.edu.au/~cscw/">Paul's CSCW and Groupware Page</a> </li>
<li><a href="http://www.eurecom.fr/~hummes/groupware.html">Project ACOST - Pointers to Groupware</a> </li>
<li><a href="http://www.brill.com/intranet/">The Intranet Journal</a> </li>
</ul>
<h2>Newsgroups and Listservers</h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="news:comp.groupware">comp.groupware</a> </li>
<li><b>MBA660</b> - The listserver for the CIS 490 class. To subscribe, send the following email message to <i>listproc@bilbo.isu.edu</i>: </li>
<li>In the body of the message, type the following only: <ul>
<li>subscribe MBA660 [your first and last name] </li>
<li>For example, I would type: <ul>
<li>subscribe mba660 Kregg Aytes </li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>Once you have subscribed and want to send a message to the class, send it to: </li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>mba660@bilbo.isu.edu </li>
</ul>
</li>
<li>If you come across other web sites, newsgroups, or listservers that you think would be of interest to others, send a note to <a href="mailto: aytekreg@fs.isu.edu">aytekreg@fs.isu.edu</a>. </li>
</ul>
</body>

