<font size=2>
<p>The Curriculum Program includes searchable information on all kinds of 
teaching materials including syllabi, bibliographies, lecture notes, 
assignments, reading lists, and textbooks. The course materials have been 
cataloged according to the American Computing Machinery (ACM) computer 
science and computer information systems curricula.
</font>
<br>
</td></tr>

<tr><td colspan=2>
<hr width=425 align=left>
</td></tr>

<tr><td colspan=2>
<font size=2><b>Standard Keyword Search</b>

<p>
This search includes ONLY those pages that are part of the Microsoft 
Academic Cooperative. It does not search all Microsoft pages or any other pages 
at Idaho State University.  Type in the words that you would like 
to search for in the text entry box, separated by AND or OR. For example, 
try examples AND curriculum OR tools.
<br></font>
</td></tr>

