<a name="dream">
<IMG SRC="gifs/drmpack.gif" ALT="Programmer's Dream Pack" ALIGN=BOTTOM WIDTH="425" HEIGHT="25" BORDER="0"></a>

<p>

<font size=2>
It includes best-selling Windows-based development tools to get you started building state-of-the-art Web sites and Internet applications with ActiveX&#153; controls. ActiveX is a set of open technologies that move the Internet beyond static documents and provide users with a more active, exciting, and useful experience. The Programmer's Dream Pack provides the best tools and information resources with which to build your programming classes and help students launch their careers.
</font>

<P>

<font size=3><b>Programmer's Dream Pack Price</b></font>
<p>

<font size=2>
Best of all, it's only $229*--you'll save substantially 
from the estimated retail price of the individual products! 
</font>
<p>

