		</tr>
		</table>

<P>

<font size=2>
<B>Microsoft Visual FoxPro&#153; 3.0</b><BR>
The Visual FoxPro database combines the 
ease of visual development and the power of FoxPro in a 32-bit Xbase 
rapid application development (RAD) tool that is fully object-oriented and 
has integrated client/server capabilities. It leverages 16-bit Windows 3.1 
and 32-bit Windows NT and Windows 95.</font><P>
 
