<P>
<font size=2>
<B>Microsoft FrontPage&#153; 1.1</b><BR>
Designed for non-programmers, yet robust 
enough even for experienced Web site developers, Microsoft FrontPage Web 
authoring and management tool version 1.1 is the fast, easy way to create 
and manage professional-quality Web sites. With easy-to-use functionality 
such as WYSIWYG editing, wizards to step you through the creation of your 
Web site, and integration with Microsoft Office, it's never been easier to 
publish on the Web!
