<font size=2>
<P>
</font><font size=3><B>Operating Systems</b></font><font size=2><P>


<B>Microsoft Windows 95</b><BR>
Microsoft Windows 95, a fully integrated 32-bit operating system, offers 
robust performance and speed, integrated networking, enhanced multimedia, mobile features, and 
Plug and Play simplicity. Characterized by an easy-to-use interface, it increases user productivity as it delivers the power needed to get the job done.
<P>
<B>Microsoft Windows NT Workstation version 4.0</b><BR>
Microsoft Windows NT Workstation 4.0 is the most powerful desktop operating system for business computing, combining the ease of Windows 95 with the reliability and security of Windows NT. Windows NT Workstation 4.0 provides easy, secure access to the Internet and corporate Intranets and is designed to be easy to manage and control in a corporate networking environment.
<P>
