<font size=2>
<p>The Curriculum Program includes searchable information on all kinds of 
teaching materials including syllabi, bibliographies, lecture notes, 
assignments, reading lists, and textbooks. The course materials have been 
cataloged according to the American Computing Machinery (ACM) computer 
science and computer information systems curricula.
</font>
<br>
</td></tr>

