<H2><A NAME="A1_2">Scheduling the Simplot Center</A></H2>

<P>
The center can be scheduled by contacting Jim Frost at (208) 236-4549
Or send e-mail to <A HREF="mailto:Frost@sdsc.isu.edu">Jim Frost (Frost@sdsc.isu.edu)</A>
<P>
Ask about our frequent users or patron pricing schedule! <HR>

<H2><A NAME="A1_3">Scheduling the portable decision support center
</A></H2>

<P>
The Center for Decision Support has the ability to deploy a fully
operational support center to your facility. In addition to deploying
locally, we have hosted sessions in Washington, DC, San Francisco,
CA, Salt Lake City, UT, Baltimore, MD, Toronto, Canada, and Seattle,
WA.
<P>
The portable center can be scheduled by contacting Jim Frost at
(208) 236-4549 Or send e-mail to <A HREF="mailto:Frost@sdsc.isu.edu">Jim Frost (Frost@sdsc.isu.edu)</A>
<P>
<CENTER>Ask about our frequent users or patron pricing schedule!</CENTER>
<HR>

