<TITLE>OTA Publications</TITLE>
<H1>OTA Publications</H1>
<HR>
<h2>General Information</h2>
<ul>
<li><A HREF="doctypes.html">Document Types</A><p>
<li><b>The complete OTA Catalog of Publications, 1972-94 is available in two parts:</b>
<a href="catag.html">A through G</a> and <a href="cathz.html">H through Z</a>
</ul><P>
<hr>
<h2>Electronic Copies</h2>
<ul>
<li><A HREF="T81.html">Report Briefs</a> are short summaries of OTA reports.<p>
<li><A HREF="publst.html">Selected Publications</a> are available in electronic form.</a>
</ul>
<p>
<hr>
<h2>How to Obtain Paper Copies</h2>
Paper copies of OTA reports can be ordered through the <A HREF="gpo.html">Government Printing Office</A> and the <A HREF="ntis.html">National Technical Information Service</A>.  OTA publications can be purchased at <A HREF="bkstores.html">U.S. government bookstores</A> and can also be borrowed from over 1400 <A HREF="library.html">libraries</A>.  <P>
