<TITLE>Work in Progress</TITLE>
<H1>Work in Progress</H1>

<HR>
<P> Listed below, by program name, is descriptive information about assessments currently in progress 
at OTA.  Information for each assessment includes title, abstract, 
project director and phone number, estimated publication date, and 
requesting committees.  The project publication dates for ongoing 
work are the best current estimates but they are subject to change 
both to allow for uncertainties inherent in research, and because 
OTA must frequently shift its priorities to match evolving congressional 
needs.
<P>
</HTML>
<UL>
<LI><B><A HREF="etiongo.html">Energy, Transportation, and Infrastructure</A></B>
<LI><B><A HREF="issongo.html">International Security & Space</A></B>
<LI><B><A HREF="itcongo.html">Industry, Telecommunications, & Commerce</A></B>
<LI><B><A HREF="ehrongo.html">Education & Human Resources</A></B>
<LI><B><A HREF="envongo.html">Environment</A></B>
<LI><B><A HREF="hltongo.html">Health</A></B>
</UL>

