<TITLE>Contacting OTA</TITLE>
<H1>Contacting OTA</H1>
<hr>
<UL>
<LI><B>Congressional Staff:  Phone 4-9241 or email cpa@ota.gov.</B><P>
<LI><B><A HREF="address.html">General Mailing Addresses and Telephone Numbers</A></B><P> 
<LI><B><A HREF="listserv.html">Receiving OTA announcements by electronic mail</A></B>: 
OTA's ListServer and other mailing lists<P>
<LI><B>Electronic mail</B>: 
All OTA staff are accessible via Internet electronic mail.  OTA electronic mail 
addresses consist of the first initial and full last name combined with "@ota.gov".
For example, in order to reach an OTA staff member named John Smith, you would
address mail to "jsmith@ota.gov".<P>
</UL>

