<H1></H1>

<H1>Appendix II: Variable Naming Standards</H1>

<H2>Variable Naming Standards</H2>

<P>
<FONT SIZE=2>Variables of the specified type should begin with
the specific extension followed by a variable name that matches
the function of the variable.  Please note, this is not an inclusive
list of  all variable types in Visual Basic.  Other types are
the discretion of the individual programmer.  These are defined
to ease the debugging and grading processes.<BR>
</FONT>
<TABLE BORDER=1>

<TR><TD WIDTH=295><B>Variable Type</B></TD><TD WIDTH=295><B>Naming convention  </B>
</TD></TR>

<TR><TD WIDTH=295>Global Variables</TD><TD WIDTH=295>GLB</TD>
</TR>

<TR><TD WIDTH=295>Static Variables</TD><TD WIDTH=295>STA</TD>
</TR>

<TR><TD WIDTH=295>Public Variables (Public to a specific Form / Module)
</TD><TD WIDTH=295>PUB</TD></TR>

<TR><TD WIDTH=295>Public Constants</TD><TD WIDTH=295>PC</TD></TR>

<TR><TD WIDTH=295>Global Constants</TD><TD WIDTH=295>GC</TD></TR>

<TR><TD WIDTH=295>Variables pass on the command line of a procedure / function
</TD><TD WIDTH=295>P_</TD></TR>

<TR><TD WIDTH=295>Typed Records</TD><TD WIDTH=295>REC_</TD></TR>

</TABLE>

<H2>Variable Naming Samples</H2>

<H3>The Following Define Global Constants</H3>

<P>
<FONT SIZE=2>Global Const GCTest as integer</FONT>
<P>
<FONT SIZE=2>Global Const GCFileHandle as integer</FONT>
<H3>The Following Define Global Varables</H3>

<P>
<FONT SIZE=2>Global GLBISActive as string</FONT>
<P>
<FONT SIZE=2>Global GLBAllowExit as integer</FONT>
<H2>Object Naming Standards</H2>

<TABLE BORDER=1>

<TR><TD WIDTH=295><B>Object Type</B></TD><TD WIDTH=295><B>Naming Convention</B>
</TD></TR>

<TR><TD WIDTH=295>Form</TD><TD WIDTH=295>FRM</TD></TR>

<TR><TD WIDTH=295>Command Button / 3D Command Button</TD><TD WIDTH=295>CMD
</TD></TR>

<TR><TD WIDTH=295>List Box</TD><TD WIDTH=295>LST</TD></TR>

<TR><TD WIDTH=295>Combo Box</TD><TD WIDTH=295>CMB</TD></TR>

<TR><TD WIDTH=295>Text Box</TD><TD WIDTH=295>TXT</TD></TR>

<TR><TD WIDTH=295>Picture Box</TD><TD WIDTH=295>PIC</TD></TR>

<TR><TD WIDTH=295>Label / 3D Label</TD><TD WIDTH=295>LBL</TD>
</TR>

<TR><TD WIDTH=295>Grid Control</TD><TD WIDTH=295>GRD</TD></TR>

