<TITLE>OTA Assessment Process</TITLE>
<H1>OTA Assessment Process</H1>
<HR>

<IMG SRC="capitol.gif"><P>
<H3>Pre-request conversations with committee members and staff</H3><BR><P><HR>

<IMG SRC="request.gif"><P>
<H3>Formal Request</H3><BR><P><HR>

<IMG SRC="proposal.gif"><P>
<H3>Proposal</H3><BR><P><HR>

<IMG SRC="approval.gif"><P>
<H3>TAB Approval</H3><BR><P><HR>

<IMG SRC="panel.gif"><P>
<H3>Selection of Advisory Panel</H3><BR><P><HR>

<IMG SRC="plan.gif"><P>
<H3>Project plan, data collection,and analysis</H3>
<UL>
<LI>Advisory panel meetings
<LI>Contractor reports
<LI>Briefings
<LI>Surveys, site visits, etc.
<LI>Workshops
</UL>
<BR><P><HR>

<IMG SRC="draft.gif"><P>
<H3>Draft final report</H3>
<UL>
<LI>Staff drafts report
<LI>In-house review
<LI>External peer review
<LI>Revision
<LI>Transmission to Director and TAB for approval
</UL>
<BR><P><HR>

<IMG SRC="report.gif"><P>
<H3>Release Summary and full report</H3>
<UL>
<LI>Embargoed press packet (press release and fact sheet)
<LI>Press conference
<LI>Mailings to
<UL>
<LI>Congress
<LI>Study participants
<LI>Interested parties
<LI>Libraries
</UL>
<LI>Electronic dissemination
</UL>
<BR><P><HR>

<IMG SRC="press.gif"><P>
<H3>Report coverage</H3>
<UL>
<LI>Science press
<LI>Popular press, radio, TV
<LI>Professional associations/newsletters
<LI>Information services
</UL>
<BR><P><HR>

<IMG SRC="action.gif"><P>
<H3>Policy action</H3>
<UL>
<LI>Congressional hearings
<LI>Briefings and informal talks with committee members and staff
<LI>Possible legislative action
<LI>OTA outreach and dissemination
<UL>
<LI>Interaction with staff of executive branch agencies
<LI>Addresses to various communities
</UL>
</UL>
<BR><P><HR>

<IMG SRC="followup.gif"><P>
<H3>Possible follow-on activities</H3>
<UL>
<LI>Supporting documents
<LI>More congressional testimony
<LI>Request for new assessment
</UL>
<BR><P>
