<TITLE>OTA Publications Catalog:  A through G</TITLE> 
<H1>Catalog of Publications, 1972-1994<br>
A through G</H1>

Publications are arranged by subject, and in reverse chronological order within 
each subject area.  Bibliographic information is provided for all titles, 
including publication date, number of pages, summary availability, and order 
numbers for both the <A HREF="gpo.html">Government Printing Office</A>
and the <A HREF="ntis.html">National Technical Information Service</A>.  Publications that are available electronically can be accessed through the<A HREF="publst.html"> Selected Publications</A> section.<p>

