<HTML>
<TITLE>GPO Ordering Information</TITLE>
<H2>GPO Ordering Information</H2>
<hr>
To order from the Superintendent of Documents of the Government 
Printing Office (GPO) call:

<BLOCKQUOTE>
(202) 512-1800
</BLOCKQUOTE>

Indicate the title, GPO stock number, quantity, and VISA, MasterCard, 
or prepaid Superintendent of Documents deposit account number.  You 
may also call one of the <A HREF="bkstores.html">GPO Bookstores</A> nearest you.<P>

You can also order by mail or fax:<P>

<BLOCKQUOTE>
Superintendent of Documents<BR>
U.S. Government Printing Office<BR>
P.O. Box 371954<BR>
Pittsburgh, PA  15250-7954<BR>
<BR>
FAX:  (202) 512-2250<BR>
</BLOCKQUOTE>

Shipping and handling charges are included in the price.  Federal 
Express service is available for an additional $8.50 per order.<P>

<A HREF="overseas.html">Overseas orders</A> 
require different order instructions and payment.

