<HTML>
<TITLE>NTIS Ordering Information</TITLE>
<H2>NTIS Ordering Information</H2>
<hr>
OTA publications are also available in either paper or microfiche 
from the National Technical Information Service.  Orders may be placed 
using an NTIS deposit account, VISA, MasterCard, American Express, 
or government purchase order.  To confirm prices and place an order:<P>

<BLOCKQUOTE>
Call (703) 487-4650<BR>
Rush orders (1-800) 553-NTIS<BR>
</BLOCKQUOTE>

A few OTA assessment reports have accompanying contractor documents 
or working papers (availability indicated by + in the citation in 
the <i>Catalog of Publications</i>).  (<i>See</i> :  <A HREF="catag.html">Catalog A through G</a> and <a href="cathz.html">Catalog H through Z</a>.)  Contractor documents and working 
papers are only available from NTIS.  Call the number above for information.<P>

