<TITLE>The Depository Library Program</TITLE>
<H2>The Depository Library Program</H2>
<hr>
Most OTA reports are distributed automatically to over 1,400 Regional 
Depository Libraries throughout the country and may be included in 
the Government Documents collection of university and public libraries 
in your area.  Consult your local librarian for additional information 
or contact:<P>

<BLOCKQUOTE>
Library Services Program<BR>
U.S. Government Printing Office<BR>
Washington, DC  20401-9325<BR>
(202) 512-1114<BR>
</BLOCKQUOTE>

