<TITLE>EHR Assessment Activities</TITLE>
<H2><A HREF="ehr.html">Education and Human Resources Program</A></H2>
<HR>
<H3><B>Assessments in Progress:</B></H3>
<P>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="#res">Residential Technologies for Elderly People and People 
with Disabilities (R)</A>
<LI><A HREF="#work">Technology and Work-Based Learning (R)</A>
<LI><A HREF="#genome">The Human Genome Project and Patenting Human DNA Sequences (R)</A>
